<br>
Basic strategy sez: <br>
- Hit until you have 17, if dealer shows 7 or above. This is because there are far more 10s in the deck than any other values, and thus, the dealer's other card is most likely to be a 10. <br>
- Hit till 13, if the dealer shows 2 or 3. <br>
- Hit till 12, if the dealer shows 4, 5 or 6. <br>
<br>
Thus, the worst possible hand that you can have, if the dealer shows 7 or above, is 16: it is too weak to win against the dealer's hand, but is also the most likely to bust... <br>
<br>
By splitting the hand, you get rid of the worst possible hand you can have, and of course, the most likely card to complement your 8s are 10s. <br>
<br>
